Brad,

Try a salvage yard. Grab the under hood insulation from a BMW, Mercedes Benz or even a water cooled VW. Cut to fit. It's made to be over a hot engine. Not sure on how to attach it, maybe expanded mesh aluminum or spray adhesive? 

